videos.headline: Musselman admits Hogs' comeback vs. Mizzou wasn't easy
videos.description: Despite a poor shooting night and playing shorthanded, Eric Musselman says No. 13 Arkansas gutted it out in coming from 17 down to beat No. 20 Missouri, 74-68.
